						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the garden adjoining the tank at Chauḷikēri.</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record registers some gifts of land, the details of which are however lost. The extant portion refers to the date <hi rend="bold">śu. 15, Wednesday,</hi> the other details of which are also lost.</p>						

						</summary>
